{"tid":41083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫幫手] 我件產品叫咩名好","createTime":"2016-12-15T15:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T23:07:26.000Z","uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d17f69a42ad5f48bb139f4a867884cf3d03f50","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"之前係高登開左個廢青創業post，有睇既巴打應該知係咩黎，依而家既進度3月左右就可以面世，我幫個產品定左個系列叫便攜式家用風扇，而中文名叫溫黛，英文叫Wenda/Wanda，不過前幾日想幫個名註冊商標果陣發現英文有人用左，只可以用中文名，但是係部風扇刻個中文有d怪，鬼佬又睇唔明，所以想改過第二個，唔知巴打絲打們有咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你提議既名被採用，產品面世果陣會送你一部full set既便攜式家用風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c588ae97813131ed3ac45e92fd9eea618cb65eba","tid":41083,"uid":36459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"Wonderful?"},{"pid":"e415694c5b9a60611f6741bd3de68b28682471b8","tid":41083,"uid":36459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Wonder<del>ful</del>?</blockquote><br />\nWonderFan"},{"pid":"cc517487fac2a1a21825bc838640bba0f4313d38","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Wonderful?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有諗過Wonder，但係都比人用左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48909a97fcb358e6e4bce0683af65415c340d562","tid":41083,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"bigwind"},{"pid":"41ad4e0dcd0a9ea530661997bfc90502015ed2a8","tid":41083,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"Wendi<br />\nWander<br />\nWanderer<br />\nWandle<br />\nWanderful <br />\nWandering jew"},{"pid":"2179d89a6b7227cd47e9169379be1b7d6fc381bd","tid":41083,"uid":6561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"wande