一定要有fan或者wind字係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗呀，可以成個名中文同英文重新諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有冇話想帶出咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612009796cbd31924e80baf9b6c8899121374b6c","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"品牌叫FutureLife  簡稱FL<br />\nLogo係咁樣，可以參考下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/000905_b253978393e8b419a01ab99161b5d28a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F000905_b253978393e8b419a01ab99161b5d28a.jpg&h=2ec20a86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73cd3c3528ce4a06c766d9edb6dffee34638bb62","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">飛廉</span>，亦作蜚廉，是中國神話中的神獸，掌管風，被稱為風伯（風神），其形象為鳥身鹿頭或者鳥頭鹿身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A3%9E%E5%BB%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25A3%259E%25E5%25BB%2589&d=fjFj6EJ132DHupDyyeTteWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=13d05e63\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A3%9E%E5%BB%89</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，風神，我第一個名就係諗左呢個，個英文好型，不過中文有少少大陸feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a700ba87e04862ad4777880881d1fc407ae53b6e","tid":41083,"uid":37736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"What the fan<br />\nWhatthefan <br />\nWtdefan"},{"pid":"aab4936e2b837a4cb4b0194ea5e4d5664573c2a2","tid":41083,"uid":5827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"Fan"},{"pid":"eaef68b84df061acf357dad70ed6a313cd2eee78","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實洗唔洗一定要有fan或者wind字係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗呀，可以成個名中文同英文重新諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有冇話想帶出咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢部風扇係新概念，有別於傳統風扇，係家用風扇同手提風扇既結合品，原本改做溫黛係因為大風，香港人熟悉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果想帶出意思既話應該有<br />\n創新<br />\n劃時代<br />\n型<br />\n大風<br />\n冇缺點<br />\n未來"},{"pid":"ae238d12895a472f2bec814838f4635f9a9bf940","tid":41083,"uid":6561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"fairyfan或者就咁fairy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfairy呢個字應該都符合到你便攜嘅意思掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfad3953010c60583475c9edb6980960ee61ea32","tid":41083,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"WANDOI"},{"pid":"fc6e4def4a95ebf387e02eafca206241f88de497","tid":41083,"uid":50,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"隨風"},{"pid":"18f59514e0b847ebfef52cd6500c253bb4e8283e","tid":41083,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe7759f23401009ebf889c3b7a048c064f4663f7","tid":41083,"uid":39268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:32:59.000Z","msg":"FANtastic<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5126d6ba40dd4b5a508c2ed5825c7dc7aa96c9e","tid":41083,"uid":37736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"WanDai"},{"pid":"cf38316f7e77b5a42f0c2527d3ff86b