怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043dc8d495d44b427d95ad0ca009f7270567b713","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一於中文叫刺風/次風/廁風/翅風，英文就叫seafood，取其偕音為賜褔，一定大賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翅風 seafood <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ba0da5bd3a259e750b77102ec835700da8cd11","tid":41083,"uid":17023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"ifan <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d324367630c83929d413a95be777a3a611f6f030","tid":41083,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一於中文叫刺風/次風/廁風/翅風，英文就叫seafood，取其偕音為賜褔，一定大賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翅風 seafood <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國大把有風既產品都唔係一定用用wind，會用wing，因為佢地愛自由，想有翼有翅膀同埋夠型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上香港人崇洋心態，唔會發掘湖流只會追隨潮流，好似咩b-duck，chocolate既香港品牌喺香港創業收哂皮，去外國出名回流返黎香港就名牌咁，<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使諗咁多含義，香港人好膚淺，唔會諗咁多內裏既含義，年輕人只鍾意追潮流要型要扮成熟大個，老一輩就要平要實用要意頭"},{"pid":"f46253c6bd420dda3097f694cd6273ab2e57a51f","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一於中文叫刺風/次風/廁風/翅風，英文就叫seafood，取其偕音為賜褔，一定大賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翅風 seafood <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國大把有風既產品都唔係一定用用wind，會用wing，因為佢地愛自由，想有翼有翅膀同埋夠型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上香港人崇洋心態，唔會發掘湖流只會追隨潮流，好似咩b-duck，chocolate既香港品牌喺香港創業收哂皮，去外國出名回流返黎香港就名牌咁，<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使諗咁多含義，香港人好膚淺，唔會諗咁多內裏既含義，年輕人只鍾意追潮流要型要扮成熟大個，老一輩就要平要實用要意頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係你咁諗，你覺得Wing 加唔加s好？ 呢個幾貼切到同埋係我個中文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de77ce048022b99d1172fab23a90d0b9393b89c0","tid":41083,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:00:38.000Z","msg":"FanCoolVer<br />\nCoolzy<br />\nCoolazy<br />\nCoolaxy"},{"pid":"c5e829601a97f8ac197c883f468d4221c5e3a527","tid":41083,"uid":20,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翅風 seafood <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國大把有風既產品都唔係一定用用wind，會用wing，因為佢地愛自由，想有翼有翅膀同埋夠型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上香港人崇洋心態，唔會發掘湖流只會追隨潮流，好似咩b-duck，chocolate既香港品牌喺香港創業收哂皮，去外國出名回流返黎香港就名牌咁，<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使諗咁多含義，香港人好膚淺，唔會諗咁多內裏既含義，年輕人只鍾意追潮流要型要扮成熟大個，老一輩就要平要實用要意頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係你咁諗，你覺得Wing 加唔加s好？ 呢個幾貼切到同埋係我個中文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但 s 呢啲字，首次字典有，人地好難先search到你，所以我改外從來唔想字典有嘅名<br />\n<br />\n- Skype / Whatsapp / Flickr ... etc<br />\n<br />\n每個產品名，都最好係可以有2-3音節出到音就最好嗱<br />\n<br />\n利申：禺見"},{"pid":"60e69ebbfda86126bcbebfa8255b16ebd52cb4fc","tid":41083,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:41:43.000Z","msg":"叫溫黛會唔會令人聯想到d唔好的野<br />\n即係唔好意頭<br />\n例如死人 家破人亡"},{"pid":"fe0d8ef6139a7c4ef210311b6518a629c434ee84","tid":41083,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"The籮of the wing<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc2f762ecb703a99ce1fe0a299697cd197e4aad","tid":41083,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"Wing+<br />\nFL Wing"},{"pid":"6959498e3901bc73abfda9443f2d57c242d40ca