者 Fujin 亦都唔型, 仲要令人聯想起神風敢死隊 Kamikaze<br />\n<br />\n印度神話有 Vayu 幾簡潔, 可以考慮, 但係有其他product(遙控飛機)用過呢個名<br />\n<br />\n我覺得亦可以用某種古語言或者某種未來世界故事(如star wars, star trek)既語言中既&quot;風&quot;字去做product名, google下應該唔難搵"},{"pid":"ae48d92c785ff487f538eff460fc2b0f53dc67f9","tid":41083,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"Hi 同學仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ca9c11685b87f6e2c13f605e735f0ea0f49c36","tid":41083,"uid":41490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:07:15.000Z","msg":"Vantage"},{"pid":"7c2119cd5c1f36bc22ac23a8afe280bfc4fab635","tid":41083,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"毛包風，mobile風，手提風<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d76e663d708d1bb60008cd064f96b5eba9a971","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fanda<br />\nFanta<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFanda唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e50394a3a3deaf2060eaffafad05ccb8918ea4","tid":41083,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果用風神做參考, 而又想打入外國市場, 可以利用外國神話人物<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_wind_deities\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_wind_deities&d=fjFj6EJ132DHupDyyeTteWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8aa0d032\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_wind_deities</a><br />\n<br />\n希臘神話 有風神 Aeolus 都算特別, 唔難讀, 有一唔好處係google過發現有電腦機箱用風扇model已經用過呢個名<br />\n其餘有Boreas, Notus等可供選擇, 不過留意到好似有風扇用緊呢D名<br />\n<br />\n羅馬有Venti, 同ventilation 聯繫較大, 同樣有以上問題<br />\n<br />\n日本風神- 志那都比古神 Shinatsuhikokami 太長, 就咁風神 Kaze-no-kami 或者 Fujin 亦都唔型, 仲要令人聯想起神風敢死隊 Kam